original_title: Couples II: More COLT Men On The Make
overview: Like your Colt studs two at a time? Then "Colt Couples II" is for you. This man-on-man DVD features some of the hottest one-on-one action in Colt's library. Here in Couples II, get a full load of classic Colt Men Ray Dragon and Felipe's man-love encounter, watch as Colt Man Carlos Moralas gets all of Colt Man Exclusive Tod Parker, after which Tod plows right into hot action with red-hot Colt Man Todd Maxwell. Finally, as if you needed any more stimulation, blow out your circuits to uber-sexy Colt Man Jake Andrews as he takes in every inch of his equally muscled partner, Colt Man Cannon.
title: Couples II: More COLT Men On The Make
